;----------foundation properties---------
m m group bedrock
prop d d_bedrock b b_bedrock s s_bedrock c c_bedrock f f_bedrock dilation &
 di_bedrock tension t_bedrock por p_bedrock perm pe_bedrock group bedrock
m m group lalluvium
prop d d_alluvium b b_alluvium s s_alluvium c c_alluvium f f_alluvium &
 dilation di_alluvium tension t_alluvium por p_alluvium perm pe_alluvium &
 group lalluvium
m m group ralluvium
prop d d_alluvium b b_alluvium s s_alluvium c c_alluvium f f_alluvium &
 dilation di_alluvium tension t_alluvium por p_alluvium perm pe_alluvium &
 group ralluvium
interface 1 aside from 136,25 to 136,11 bside from 136,25 to 136,11
interface 1 glued kn=k1 ks=k1
interface 2 aside from 136,11 to 138,11 bside from 136,11 to 138,11
interface 2 glued kn=k2 ks=k2
interface 3 aside from 138,11 to 138,25 bside from 138,11 to 138,25
interface 3 glued kn=k3 ks=k3
m m group groutcurtain
